                <head>No. 58<lb/>
                    <hi rend="italic">Editorial Note</hi>
                </head>
                <p>An agreement between the United States and the Republic of China, concerning the
                    status of the United States Military Assistance Advisory Group, was effected by
                    an exchange of notes signed at Taipei on October 23 and November 1, 1952; the
                    text may be found in 3 <gloss target="#t_UST1">UST</gloss> (pt. 4) 5166.</p>
            </div>
